                                             , '{*.|Belt*|Capply|Capstrip|Greentyre|Innerliner|Innerliner_assembly|Pre_Assembly|Ply*|Rubberstrip|Sidewall*|Tread|Tyre|Vulcanized_tyre|Tyre_vulcanized, *.Tread.Compound|Tread_compound, *.Capstrip.Capply, *.Ply*|Belt*.Racknumber|Composite }'
